<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>엔씨테크</title>
    <style>
        *{
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        @media (max-width: 755px){
            .main-content{
                display:block;
                border: 1px solid rgb(207, 207, 207);
                height:240px;
                margin:10px;
                width:90%;
            }
            #main-container{
                justify-content: center;
                display:flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                margin:auto;
                padding-left: 5%;
                width:1280px;
            }
            #mimg{
                content: url("/img/m_mainlogo.jpg");
            }
            #mimg2{
                content: url("./img/m_mainlogo2.png");
            }
        }
        @media (min-width: 755px){
            #mimg{
                content: url("./img/mainlogo.jpg");
            }
            #mimg2{
                content: url("./img/mainlogo2.png");
            }
            .main-content{
                display:inline-block;
                margin:10px 20px 10px 20px;
                height: 240px;
                width:33%;
                border: 1px solid rgb(207, 207, 207);
            }
            #main-container{
                justify-content: center;
                display:flex;
                margin:auto;
                width:1280px;
            }
        }
        #container{
            display: flex;
            width: 100%;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

       
        @keyframes fade {
            0% {opacity: 0;}
            5% {opacity: 1;}
            45% {opacity: 1;}
            50% {opacity: 1;}
            80% {opacity: 0;}
        }

        section{
            height:300px;
        }

        main{
            display:flex;
            width:100%;
        }

        .main-content>img{
            width:100%;
            height:81.5%;
            cursor:grab;
        }
       
        #main-content2{
            display:inline-block;
            margin:10px 20px 10px 20px;
            height: 240px;
            width:33%;     
        }

        main p{
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.438);
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        #main-log{
            position: relative;
            display:flex;
            justify-content: center;
            width:100%;
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin:auto;
            height:450px;
        }
        #main-log img{
            position:absolute;
            top:0;bottom:0;
            text-align: center;
            width:100%;
            max-width: 1280px;
            height:100%;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fade 8s infinite;
            object-fit: cotain;
        }
        #main-log img:nth-child(1) {
           animation-delay: 0s;
        }

        #main-log img:nth-child(2) {
            animation-delay: 3s;
        }
        
    </style>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/stylecss.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/stylecss2.css">
    <script>
        function estimateclick(){
            window.location.href="/estimate?page=1";
        }
        function productclick(){
            window.location.href="/product?page=1";
        }
    </script>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="container">
        <header>
            <%- include("header.ejs") %>
            <div id="main-log">
                <img id="mimg">
                <img id="mimg2">
           </div>
            
        <section>
            <main>
                <div id="main-container">
                    <div class="main-content">
                        <p>견적문의</p>
                        <img src="./img/estimate.jpg" onclick="estimateclick()">
                    </div>
                    <div class="main-content">
                        <p>제품소개</p>
                        <img src="./img/product.jpg" onclick="productclick()">
                    </div>
                    <div class="main-content">
                        <p style="margin-bottom:60px">회사정보</p>
                        <span style="margin-left:10px">인천광역시 서구 가정로16번길 19</span><br>
                        <span style="color:blue;margin-left:10px;">TEL : 010-9088-3648</span><br>
                        <span style="margin-left:10px">E-mail : nts31@hanmail.com</span><br>
                        <span style="margin-left:10px">금속 케이스 전문 제조업체</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </main>
            <aside>
                
            </aside>
        </section>
        <footer>
            <%- include("footer.ejs") %>
        </footer>
    </div>
    


</body>

</html>